  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t來源<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS8yMkhvbW9Qb2xpdGljdXMvc3RhdHVzLzE3NDQ5MTk2MzM0MjM5MDQ5MDQ_\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/22HomoPoliticus/status/1744919633423904904?\">https://twitter.com/22HomoPoliticus/status/1744919633423904904?</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjkzNTE3MDgwMjIyMDE1MzJhYTgzLmpwZz93aWR0aD01NjEmaGVpZ2h0PTUzNQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/69351708022201532aa83.jpg?width=561&amp;height=535\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/69351708022201532aa83.jpg?width=561&amp;height=535\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/69351708022201532aa83.jpg?width=561&amp;height=535\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n該貼文是在今月（1月）10日披露出的，也就是早於王支安在脫口秀羞辱身障人士之前的發言<br/>\n<br/>\r\n該事件後續以及王支安的囂張嘴臉：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9NaWxpdGFyeV9pZHZfdHcvc3RhdHVzLzE3NTAzMTExMzY0OTMxOTU3MjY_\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/Military_idv_tw/status/1750311136493195726?\">https://twitter.com/Military_idv_tw/status/1750311136493195726?</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n如果此事件真的讓王支安失去獲得日本國籍資格的話，那也只能說“活該”\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
